      <item>
        <title>Chalk sample post with all elements</title>
        <description>&lt;p&gt;Chalk uses the default Jekyll syntax highlighting gem Rouge. It has a customized style for both light and dark theme.
Use the &lt;code class=&quot;language-plaintext highlighter-rouge&quot;&gt;highlight&lt;/code&gt; tag to use the following code highlighting your preferred language:&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;figure class=&quot;highlight&quot;&gt;&lt;pre&gt;&lt;code class=&quot;language-html&quot; data-lang=&quot;html&quot;&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;c&quot;&gt;&amp;lt;!-- This is a comment --&amp;gt;&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;span class=&quot;nt&quot;&gt;&amp;lt;div&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;na&quot;&gt;class=&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;s&quot;&gt;&quot;grid&quot;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;nt&quot;&gt;&amp;gt;&lt;/span&gt;
  &lt;span class=&quot;nt&quot;&gt;&amp;lt;h1&amp;gt;&lt;/span&gt;This is a heading&lt;span class=&quot;nt&quot;&gt;&amp;lt;/h1&amp;gt;&lt;/span&gt;
  &lt;span class=&quot;nt&quot;&gt;&amp;lt;p&amp;gt;&lt;/span&gt;
    This is a paragraph text.
  &lt;span class=&quot;nt&quot;&gt;&amp;lt;/p&amp;gt;&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;span class=&quot;nt&quot;&gt;&amp;lt;/div&amp;gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/figure&gt;

&lt;h2 id=&quot;headings&quot;&gt;Headings&lt;/h2&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Chalk includes 3 headings by default:&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;h2 id=&quot;heading-first-level&quot;&gt;Heading first level&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;h3 id=&quot;heading-second-level&quot;&gt;Heading second level&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;h4 id=&quot;heading-third-level&quot;&gt;Heading third level&lt;/h4&gt;

&lt;figure class=&quot;highlight&quot;&gt;&lt;pre&gt;&lt;code class=&quot;language-markdown&quot; data-lang=&quot;markdown&quot;&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;gu&quot;&gt;## Heading first level&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;span class=&quot;gu&quot;&gt;### Heading second level&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;span class=&quot;gu&quot;&gt;#### Heading third level&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/figure&gt;

&lt;h2 id=&quot;lists&quot;&gt;Lists&lt;/h2&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Unordered list example:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
  &lt;li&gt;Unordered list item 1&lt;/li&gt;
  &lt;li&gt;Unordered list item 2&lt;/li&gt;
  &lt;li&gt;Unordered list item 3&lt;/li&gt;
  &lt;li&gt;Unordered list item 4&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Ordered list example:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ol&gt;
  &lt;li&gt;Ordered list item 1&lt;/li&gt;
  &lt;li&gt;Ordered list item 1&lt;/li&gt;
  &lt;li&gt;Ordered list item 1&lt;/li&gt;
  &lt;li&gt;Ordered list item 1&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ol&gt;

&lt;figure class=&quot;highlight&quot;&gt;&lt;pre&gt;&lt;code class=&quot;language-markdown&quot; data-lang=&quot;markdown&quot;&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;p&quot;&gt;*&lt;/span&gt; Unordered list item 1
&lt;span class=&quot;p&quot;&gt;*&lt;/span&gt; Unordered list item 2
&lt;span class=&quot;p&quot;&gt;
1.&lt;/span&gt; Order list item 1
&lt;span class=&quot;p&quot;&gt;2.&lt;/span&gt; Order list item 1&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/figure&gt;

&lt;h2 id=&quot;emoji-support-star&quot;&gt;Emoji support :star:&lt;/h2&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Emoji’s can be used everywhere in :cat2: your markdown!&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;h2 id=&quot;quotes&quot;&gt;Quotes&lt;/h2&gt;

&lt;p&gt;A quote looks like this:&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;blockquote&gt;
  &lt;p&gt;Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet, consectetur adipisicing elit, sed do eiusmod tempor
incididunt ut labore et dolore magna.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/blockquote&gt;

&lt;figure class=&quot;highlight&quot;&gt;&lt;pre&gt;&lt;code class=&quot;language-markdown&quot; data-lang=&quot;markdown&quot;&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;gt&quot;&gt;&amp;gt; Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet, consectetur adipisicing elit, sed do eiusmod tempor&lt;/span&gt;
incididunt ut labore et dolore magna.&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/figure&gt;

&lt;h2 id=&quot;media&quot;&gt;Media&lt;/h2&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Images can be added with a default &lt;code class=&quot;language-plaintext highlighter-rouge&quot;&gt;&amp;lt;img&amp;gt;&lt;/code&gt; tag.
If you wish that an image can be enlarged on click use the image include tag. You can pass 3 variables:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
  &lt;li&gt;&lt;code class=&quot;language-plaintext highlighter-rouge&quot;&gt;path&lt;/code&gt;: Image to show in the blog post.&lt;/li&gt;
  &lt;li&gt;&lt;code class=&quot;language-plaintext highlighter-rouge&quot;&gt;path-detail&lt;/code&gt;: Image to show when enlarging.&lt;/li&gt;
  &lt;li&gt;&lt;code class=&quot;language-plaintext highlighter-rouge&quot;&gt;alt&lt;/code&gt;: Alt text for image in blog post.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;/assets/documentation/sample-image@2x-f8eae5b88a72da0c485e1c9821020764ff2c5b7d3a5c05f1e14fb2a276c07781.jpg&quot;&gt;
  &lt;img src=&quot;/assets/documentation/sample-image-0a264584b152aa8d86f61525d05ae1131787d0a1029aa1cb7e3e4148b5d34755.jpg&quot; alt=&quot;Sample image&quot; class=&quot;zooming&quot; data-rjs=&quot;/assets/documentation/sample-image@2x-f8eae5b88a72da0c485e1c9821020764ff2c5b7d3a5c05f1e14fb2a276c07781.jpg&quot; data-zooming-width=&quot;1220&quot; data-zooming-height=&quot;813&quot; /&gt;
&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;figure class=&quot;highlight&quot;&gt;&lt;pre&gt;&lt;code class=&quot;language-liquid&quot; data-lang=&quot;liquid&quot;&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;p&quot;&gt;{%&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;w&quot;&gt; &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;nt&quot;&gt;include&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;w&quot;&gt; &lt;/span&gt;image.html&lt;span class=&quot;w&quot;&gt; &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;na&quot;&gt;path&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;o&quot;&gt;=&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;s2&quot;&gt;&quot;documentation/sample-image.jpg&quot;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;err&quot;&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;w&quot;&gt;                      &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;na&quot;&gt;path-detail&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;o&quot;&gt;=&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;s2&quot;&gt;&quot;documentation/sample-image@2x.jpg&quot;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;err&quot;&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;w&quot;&gt;                      &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;na&quot;&gt;alt&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;o&quot;&gt;=&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;s2&quot;&gt;&quot;Sample image&quot;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;w&quot;&gt; &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;p&quot;&gt;%}&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/figure&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Videos can be added and are responsive by default (4x3 by default, 16x9 with extra class).&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;div class=&quot;embed-responsive embed-responsive-16by9&quot;&gt;
&lt;iframe src=&quot;https://www.youtube.com/embed/vO7m8Hre72E?modestbranding=1&amp;amp;autohide=1&amp;amp;showinfo=0&amp;amp;controls=0&quot; allowfullscreen=&quot;&quot;&gt;&lt;/iframe&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;

&lt;figure class=&quot;highlight&quot;&gt;&lt;pre&gt;&lt;code class=&quot;language-html&quot; data-lang=&quot;html&quot;&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;nt&quot;&gt;&amp;lt;div&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;na&quot;&gt;class=&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;s&quot;&gt;&quot;embed-responsive embed-responsive-16by9&quot;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;nt&quot;&gt;&amp;gt;&lt;/span&gt;
  &lt;span class=&quot;nt&quot;&gt;&amp;lt;iframe&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;na&quot;&gt;src=&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;s&quot;&gt;&quot;url-to-video&quot;&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;na&quot;&gt;allowfullscreen&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;nt&quot;&gt;&amp;gt;&amp;lt;/iframe&amp;gt;&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;span class=&quot;nt&quot;&gt;&amp;lt;/div&amp;gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/figure&gt;

</description>
