      <item>
        <title>Jekyll Release for the Holidays! v2.5.3 Out</title>
        <description>&lt;p&gt;Happy Holidays, everyone.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Jekyll v2.5.3 is a quick patch release, containing some minor fixes. See the
